==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Localization
<hw>Lo`cal*i*za"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Cf. F.
<ets>localisation</ets>.]</ety> <def>Act of localizing, or state of
being localized.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Cerebral localization</b></col> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld>,
<cd>the localization of the control of special functions, as of sight or
of the various movements of the body, in special regions of the
brain.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Localize</ent>⟦br⟧
